1.0.name: wordpress/wp-visitors
1.0.description: wp-visitors records information about every visitor (page load). Requested URL, Referring URL, IP address, Hostname and Browser along with Date/Time are recorded and displayed in a tabular fashion. Geographical resolution of IP address (it's only approximate) is also included.
